n## Kvantestartup har udviklet en chip til fremti\u00addens supercom\u00adputer \u2013 jagter nu kapital\n![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6721f6603ca1e674e1539dfb/6747274a343fd69f06893e9a_24486991-1.jpg)\n![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6721f6603ca1e674e1539db4/67220ffe36d9614e9fc0dc64_Vectors-Wrapper.svg)\n### Sparrow Quantum\nNews\nJanuary 19, 2023\nTeknologien er nu moden til, at chippen fra Sparrow Quantum kan komme ud over rampen, fort\u00e6ller Peter Lodahl (t.h.) og adm. direkt\u00f8r Kurt Stokbro.\nLink to full article: <https://borsen.dk/nyheder/virksomheder/kvantestartup-er-klar-med-sin-forste-revolutionerende-chip>\n\u200d\nNews\nJanuary 19, 2023\nInvestment from the Innovation Fund Denmark: 16.2 million kroner. \nDuration: 5 years. \nOfficial title: FTQP \u2013 \u2018Fault-Tolerant Architectures for Quantum Computing with Photon Emitters\u2019. \n![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6721f6603ca1e674e1539db4/67220ffe36d9614e9fc0dc64_Vectors-Wrapper.svg)\n### News\nStay updated with our latest news and insights. Check back regularly for updates on Sparrow Quantum and our industry.\n[![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6721f6603ca1e674e1539dfb/67f7b68c2dd249c5a7b005e8_Person%20%2B%20chip%203.jpg) News April 10, 2025 Sparrow Quantum Secures \u20ac21.5 Million to Accelerate Photonic Quantum Innovation in Europe  ](https://sparrowquantum.com/post/sparrow-quantum-secures-21-5-million-euro-to-accelerate-photonic-quantum-innovation-in-europe)\n[![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6721f6603ca1e674e1539dfb/67472d0b15de91cf03408e63_Product-bg-img-03.jpg) News May 11, 2023 Rekordstor startkapital til det danske kvanteteknologifirma, Sparrow Quantum ](https://sparrowquantum.com/post/rekordstor-startkapital-til-det-danske-kvanteteknologifirma-sparrow-quantum)\n[![](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6721f6603ca1e674e1539dfb/69b1222144f702fbe914dfd8_DSC01847%20Large.jpeg) News March 10, 2026 Forbes: Is Europe Poised To Lead the Quantum Computing Race? ](https://sparrowquantum.com/post/forbes-is-europe-poised-to-lead-the-quantum-computing-race)\n[![Sparrow Quantum logo with blue gradient color](https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6721f6603ca1e674e1539db4/6728a5364585a64f06e02a6e_Logo%20-%20Left%20Aligned.svg)](https://sparrowquantum.com/post/kvantestartup-har-udviklet-en-chip-til-fremtidens-supercomputer-jagter-nu-kapital)\nUnlocking Quantum Breakthroughs,   \nOne Photon at a Time\nAddress\n[Nordre Fasanvej 215  \n2000 Frederiksberg  \nDenmark  \nCVR. 36998717](https://maps.app.goo.gl/LhwCTfMwYQrr9w1R8)\nInfo\ninfo@sparrowquantum.com[+ 45 31 13 66 55](tel:+4531136655)[Privacy Policy](https://sparrowquantum.com/privacy-policy)\nSocials\n[LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/company/sparrow-quantum/)[X](https://x.com/sparrow_quantum)[Youtube](https://www.youtube.com/@SparrowQuantum)\n\u00a92026 - Sparrow Quantum\n",
